These are Puzzles for 7x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-3-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-milk, fanta, soy-milk
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: tulip, amaryllis, poppy, marigold
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, hiking, magic-tricks, puzzles
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, ambient, punk, hip-hop
4 different pets are kept: bird, frog, hamster, lizard
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, handball, lacrosse, surfing
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, game, bongani, blend
 1. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
 2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the person who growsmarigold##1
 3. the person who growsamaryllis is on the far left##1
 4. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the person who's sport is handball##1
 5. the fan of electronic is on the right of the fan of punk##1
 6. the bongani-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's sport is baseball##3
 7. the fan of ambient is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person who growspoppy is on the left or right of the bongani-smoker##3
 9. the owner of the frog is on the far right##1
10. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the person who growsamaryllis##3
11. the blend-smoker is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
12. the person drinking 7up is between the person who's hobby is hiking and the person who growsmarigold##2
13. the blend-smoker is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
14. the person drinking soy-milk is the owner of the hamster##1
15. the game-smoker is on the left or right of the person who growstulip##3
16. the bongani-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
17. the fan of electronic is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |       2        |      3      |      4       |
| Beverage    | soy-milk   | 7up            | almond-milk | fanta        |
| Flower        | amaryllis       | poppy         | marigold     | tulip       |
| Hobby       | hiking     | drawing        | puzzles     | magic-tricks |
| Music-Genre         | ambient     | hip-hop | punk    | electronic   |
| Pet         | hamster    | lizard         | bird        | frog         |
| Sport       | surfing    | baseball       | lacrosse    | handball     |
| Cigar   | bongani | blend     | game         | havana         |

