.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-3-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, lemonade, milk, tea
There 4 different types of food: eggplant, grapes, peach, raspberry
City: edinburgh, london, prague, nizza
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, comedy, disaster, thriller
4 different games are played: scrabble, bridge, snooker, go
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, hedgehog, lizard, snake
There are 4 different favourite colors: lilac, blood-red, emerald, black
 1. the person watching thriller movies is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
 2. the person who likes blood-red is between the person who likes black and the owner of the hedgehog##2
 3. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
 4. the person watching adventure movies is the person eating raspberry##1
 5. the person who likes emerald is on the left of the person who likes blood-red##1
 6. the owner of the hedgehog is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person eating raspberry##1
 8. the person traveling to nizza is the person eating peach##1
 9. the person eating grapes is between the person playing snooker and the person who likes emerald##2
10. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the person traveling to prague##1
11. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
12. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the owner of the guinea-pig##3
13. the person drinking milk is the person who likes lilac##1
14. the person eating eggplant is on the far right##1
15. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
16. the person watching thriller movies is the person playing scrabble##1
17. the person watching disaster movies is on the left or right of the person traveling to edinburgh##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |     3      |    4     |
